author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Shower plumbing tile tips…I’m using a diamond hole saw with a drill adapter. I set the Makita drill on speed 2 and use the template to steady/cool the hole saw. I back notch trowel the tile and use @perfectlevelmaster crosses to set the tile on the wall 🔥#tileshower #bathroomremodel #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
